name: Carrot Orange Apple Turmeric Juice
description:
For Full Recipe ~ Use QR Code

Recipe, Photos & Video by: Dr. Akala Lemus, D.C.
9/9/2018

Ingredients:
3-4 large carrots
1 orange, peeled
1 apple
1" piece of turmeric

Method:

1. Juice all ingredients using a juicer.
2. Strain juice to remove any pulp that passed through the juicer. 
3. Pour into a glass; injoy!
